## Example: School Management SaaS

### 1. Student Enrollment

**Description:** System to enroll students in the school with complete profile information

**User Stories:**
- As a school admin, I want to enroll new students so that they can access the system
- As a parent, I want to view my child's enrollment status online

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] Collect student personal information (name, DOB, gender, address)
- [ ] Assign student to a class/grade
- [ ] Generate unique student registration number
- [ ] Upload student photo
- [ ] Record parent/guardian contact information
- [ ] Send enrollment confirmation email
- [ ] Support bulk enrollment via CSV

**Priority:** High

### 2. Grade Management

**Description:** Teachers can record and manage student grades for subjects

**User Stories:**
- As a teacher, I want to enter grades for my students so that they can track progress
- As a student, I want to view my grades online

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] Teachers can enter grades by subject and term
- [ ] Support for multiple grading systems (percentage, letter grades, GPA)
- [ ] Automatic GPA calculation
- [ ] Grade reports printable as PDF
- [ ] Parents can view their child's grades
- [ ] Prevent grade modification after term is closed

**Priority:** High

### 3. Attendance Tracking

**Description:** Daily attendance recording for students

**User Stories:**
- As a teacher, I want to mark daily attendance quickly
- As a parent, I want to receive alerts when my child is absent

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] Mark students as present/absent/late
- [ ] Bulk marking (e.g., "mark all present")
- [ ] Attendance reports by student, class, or date range
- [ ] SMS/email alerts for absences
- [ ] Attendance percentage calculation
- [ ] Integration with timetable

**Priority:** Medium

