## Non-Functional Requirements

### Performance
- Page load time < 2 seconds
- Support 1000 concurrent users
- API response time < 500ms

### Security
- Multi-tenant data isolation (franchise_id filtering)
- RBAC with granular permissions
- Session timeout after 30 minutes
- Audit trail for all data modifications

### Scalability
- Support up to 100 franchises
- Support up to 10,000 students per franchise
- Cloud-ready architecture

### Usability
- Mobile-responsive design
- Support for offline data entry (sync later)
- Multi-language support (English, French, Swahili)

